data.description: Welcome to Grandview! This impressive floor plan is a 3 bedroom, single story home that includes a separate room perfect for a 4th bedroom/office or den. The exceptionally private lot provides panoramic views of the Southwest Vista Valley and majestic Mountain's. Enjoy the peaceful scenery and pristine mature landscaping. The spacious front porch and back patio are perfect places to relax. The 4 car insulated garage has an abundance of space! This home will meet all your expectations inside and out! Open house Saturday December 9th and Sunday December 10th from 1 pm to 3:30p. See optional 4th bedroom option per the builder floor plan. The 2 sheds in the back yard stay. 4 car garage includes epoxy floor, multiple shelves and cabinets with a Workbench included. Utility sink also in the garage. The Fireplace is located in the great room/Kitchen area.
